 emptyList(),\n currentTranscribedText = \"\",\n currentAssistantResponse = \"\"\n )\n }\n }\n\n override fun onCleared() {\n super.onCleared()\n tts?.stop()\n tts?.shutdown()\n speechRecognizer?.destroy()\n }\n}"}"}}]},{"role":"tool","name":"edit_file","tool_call_id":"toolu_bdrk_01U1bEE3nJ49JX5iCie7AP1M","content":"The apply model made the following changes to the file:

